title: Relaxation - Sounds of the Earth: Woodfire
description:
Sounds of the Earth:

Woodfire
--------------------

The sound of the crackling flames. It is as if you, staring into the burning wood,
sit in front of an imaginary hearth. Warm your hands and thoughts to the woodfire
sound on this album


Part 1 - 35:58

Part 2 - 36:00


Total Time: 72:01

---

Sounds of the Earth offers pure nature sounds, no voices are
added, no music is added, no human-induced noises are heard.
Sounds of the Earth bids you welcome to the wild and the
fragile sounds of nature.

---

Enjoy!
